bile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_7419392\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juni 27, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104abf1719476418454.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/abf1719476418454.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/abf1719476418454.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"liv1665702685582\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      &lt;x-subst type=\"function\"&gt;\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">XHTML placeholder that is replaced by the value of the specified ProcScript function; one of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$usp_formtitle</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$putmess</span>, or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$text</span>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"liv1665702685582__section_w671ab1b5b1_w672ab1b5_w673ab1\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104abf1719476418454_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"liv1665702685582__codeblock_ckp_5q3_wbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;x-substtype=\"function\" name=\"AllowedProcScriptFunction\"&gt;Content&lt;/x-subst&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"liv1665702685582__p_d115754e1_d115755e1_d115756e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-subst</code>\n            \n                             type\n                             <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"function\"</code>\n            \n                             name\n                             <code class=\"ph codeph\">=\"</code>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$text</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">IDString</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)\"&gt;</code>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$text</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">IDString</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">) &lt;/x-subst&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"liv1665702685582__section_zk2_xq3_wbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d590553e111\"> Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"liv1665702685582__ul_nkf_yq3_wbc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"liv1665702685582__li_d44180e1_d44181e1_d44182e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"liv1665702685582__p_d115760e1_d115761e1_d115762e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">AllowedProcScriptFunction</var>—name of the function containing the\n                  value to be substituted; can be:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"liv1665702685582__ul_okf_yq3_wbc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"liv1665702685582__li_d44183e1_d44184e1_d44185e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$usp_formtitle</span>—sets the server page title using the value of\n                        <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formtitle</span>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"liv1665702685582__li_d44186e1_d44187e1_d44188e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$putmess</span>—display the contents of the message frame .</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"liv1665702685582__li_d44189e1_d44190e1_d44191e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$text</span>—display labels with <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$text</span>. </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"liv1665702685582__li_d44192e1_d44193e1_d44194e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"liv1665702685582__p_d115763e1_d115764e1_d115765e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">IDString</var>—ID of the label text to be substituted.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"liv1665702685582__section_f34_jr3_wbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d590553e165\">$usp_formtitle</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"liv1665702685582__p_d115769e1_d115770e1_d115771e1\">The layout of a static server page typically\n            contains the following element specifying the initial server page title:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"liv1665702685582__pre_rvy_kr3_wbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;x-subst type=\"function\" name=\"$usp_formtitle\"&gt;\n &lt;title&gt;$usp_formtitle &lt;/title&gt;\n&lt;/x-subst&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"liv1665702685582__p_d115772e1_d115773e1_d115774e1\">When <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webgen</span> parses the layout,\n            it replaces the <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-subst&gt;</code> tags by:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"liv1665702685582__pre_uvy_kr3_wbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;title&gt;<var class=\"keyword varname\">ServerPageTitle</var>&lt;/title&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"liv1665702685582__p_d115775e1_d115776e1_d115777e1\">where <var class=\"keyword varname\">ServerPageTitle</var> is the\n            current value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formtitle</span>. This title is displayed in the browser\n            tab displaying the USP.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"liv1665702685582__section_fln_lr3_wbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d590553e202\">$text</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"liv1665702685582__p_d115781e1_d115782e1_d115783e1\">When using function substitution with\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$text</span>, the current value of the function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$text</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code> IDString <code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> is substituted for labels with\n               \"<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$text</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code> IDString <code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code> as their contents.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lrk1665702685508.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Substituting ProcScript Functions and Including Files in Static Server Pages</a><p>You can use the &lt;x-subst&gt; tag to substitute some ProcScript functions ($formtitle, $putmess and $text) or include files on a static server page.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xtf1665702608323.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$text</a><p>Return the text of a message or help text.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/blc1719554861507.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$putmess</a><p>Send a message to the message frame, or return the contents of the message frame.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gna1665702540285.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>webgen</a><p>Generate an XHTML document from the layout definition and the component definition of a static server page.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7419392\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7419392\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "<x-subst type=\"function\"> Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juni 27, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 <x-subst type=\"function\"> XHTML placeholder that is replaced by the value of the specified ProcScript function; one of $usp_formtitle , $putmess , or $text . Explain this code <x-substtype=\"function\" name=\"AllowedProcScriptFunction\">Content</x-subst> Copy Example: <x-subst type = \"function\" name =\" $text ( IDString )\"> $text ( IDString ) </x-subst> Arguments AllowedProcScriptFunction —name of the function containing the value to be substituted; can be: $usp_formtitle —sets the server page title using the value of $formtitle . $putmess —display the contents of the message frame . $text —display labels with $text . IDString —ID of the label text to be substituted. $usp_formtitle The layout of a static server page typically contains the following element specifying the initial server page title: <x-subst type=\"function\" name=\"$usp_formtitle\"> <title>$usp_formtitle </title> </x-subst> Copy When webgen parses the layout, it replaces the <x-subst> tags by: <title> ServerPageTitle </title> Copy where ServerPageTitle is the current value of $formtitle . This title is displayed in the browser tab displaying the USP. $text When using function substitution with $text , the current value of the function $text ( IDString ) is substituted for labels with \" $text ( IDString ) \" as their contents. Related Links Substituting ProcScript Functions and Including Files in Static Server Pages You can use the <x-subst> tag to substitute some ProcScript functions ($formtitle, $putmess and $text) or include files on a static server page. $text Return the text of a message or help text. $putmess Send a message to the message frame, or return the contents of the message frame. webgen Generate an XHTML document from the layout definition and the component definition of a static server page. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}